    <item>
      <title>警方称，在“网络绑架”计划后，中国学生在犹他州被发现安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-01/missing-chinese-exchange-student-found-safe-in-utah-following-cyber-kidnapping-scheme-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[犹他州里弗代尔（美联社）据报道，上周在犹他州失踪的一名来自中国的外国交换生被发现参与了一项明显的“网络绑架”计划，目的是向该学生的家人勒索 8 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-01/missing-chinese-exchange-student-found-safe-in-utah-following-cyber-kidnapping-scheme-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 22:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
